inputs.name: example-subnet-tags-78edd924
inputs.templateBody:
AWSTemplateFormatVersion: '2010-09-09'
                Outputs:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Value: !Ref NodeGroup
                Resources:
                    NodeGroup:
                        Type: AWS::AutoScaling::AutoScalingGroup
                        Properties:
                          DesiredCapacity: 2
                          LaunchConfigurationName: example-subnet-tags-nodeLaunchConfiguration-e2798ec
                          MinSize: 1
                          MaxSize: 2
                          VPCZoneIdentifier: ["subnet-07dd3672c8837482e","subnet-082f60dfa4fd324de","subnet-0b2e66a3ecd1e240b"]
                          Tags:
                          
                          - Key: Name
                            Value: example-subnet-tags-eksCluster-076f13e-worker
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                          - Key: kubernetes.io/cluster/example-subnet-tags-eksCluster-076f13e
                            Value: owned
                            PropagateAtLaunch: 'true'
                        UpdatePolicy:
                          AutoScalingRollingUpdate:
                            MinInstancesInService: '1'
                            MaxBatchSize: '1'
